precis:
Enactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF, 2002-6
which removes the tariff on certain polypropylene and polyethylene mesh for
mussel or onion bags, polyester nonwoven fabrics for waistbands for apparel
and polyester fabrics for sleeping bags.
